Question: Does the patient have a history of self-harm or suicidal behaviors?  If yes, specify behaviors, number of episodes, age at first occurrence, recency, lethality and intent of behaviors. Respond concisely, for example "Cutting: 3 episodes from age 15-20, most recent 6 months ago, non-lethal, impulsive intent" or "Multiple overdoses: 6 from ages 18-25, most recent 1 month ago, varying intent from impulsive to suicidal". If unknown or no history, respond "NA". Include the PDF page number(s) indicating the source of the answer. Omit any summaries before or after the response.
